name: AMD Ryzen 2700x
description: AMD's Ryzen1700X delivers incredible multi-threading and multi-tasking performance with 8 processor cores and 16 threads thanks to SMT Multithreading. Featuring true machine intelligence via AMD SenseMI technology, you can push the limits even further with Extended Frequency Range (XFR) to lift the maximum boost frequency in the presence of better cooling. REQUIRES A CPU COOLER AND DISCRETE GRAPHICS CARD, NOT INCLUDED.

name: ASUS ROG Strix Z370-E Gaming LGA1151 DDR4 DP HDMI DVI M.2 Z370 ATX Motherboard with onboard 802.11ac WiFi and USB 3.1 for 8th Generation Intel Core Processors

name: Futura 34 EL Backpack
description: With an elongated spring steel frame behind our newly innovated mesh backsystem the Futura 34 EL is the perfect choice for hikers over 6 feet tall. With all the amenities of our shorter Futura models this pack adds the extra inches so you can go the extra miles with comfort and ease.

Its unique concave standing surface enables recovery if the board tilts. Made of RAM-Xâ„¢S impact-resistant material, the VIBE 80 is built to last for many fun-filled days on the water.
